     4	/// @title FenwickTreeLibrary
     5	/// @notice Implements a 0-indexed Fenwick Tree (Binary Indexed Tree) for prefix sum operations.
     6	/// @dev Enables efficient updates and prefix sum queries over a dynamic array.
     7	///
     8	/// # Overview
     9	/// Fenwick Tree is a compact data structure optimized for cumulative frequency computations:
    10	/// - `update(i, delta)` increments the element at index `i` by signed `delta`.
    11	/// - `prefixSum(i)` returns the sum of elements in the range `[0, i]`.
    12	///
    13	/// This library provides:
    14	/// - `O(log n)` time complexity for updates and prefix queries.
    15	/// - `O(1)` fixed cost for extending the tree by doubling its capacity.
    16	/// - Support only for arrays whose lengths are powers of two (2^k).
    17	///
    18	/// # References
